489
00:38:58.708 --> 00:39:00.708
Je leek me wel zo'n schuimvinger-dame.

490
00:39:00.833 --> 00:39:01.917
Dus niet.

491
00:39:02.042 --> 00:39:03.750
Alsjeblieft.

492
