534
00:45:38.292 --> 00:45:39.250
Luister naar me.

535
00:45:39.375 --> 00:45:40.750
Kus me.

536
00:45:44.083 --> 00:45:45.383
Je moet nu gaan.

537
00:45:56.625 --> 00:45:58.292
Haal haar hier weg.

538
00:46:15.375 --> 00:46:16.675
