539
00:46:18.250 --> 00:46:19.550
Haal haar nu weg.

540
00:46:21.250 --> 00:46:22.550
Schiet hem neer.

541
00:46:26.833 --> 00:46:28.133
Haal haar weg.

542
00:46:30.583 --> 00:46:31.883
Voer haar af.

543
00:47:22.458 --> 00:47:23.758
